WEBVTT

00:03:31.486 --> 00:03:37.577
Christmas Eve, Talk about Shri Jesus, Ganapatipule, India, 24.12.1990

00:03:37.779 --> 00:03:44.670
So today’s the Christmas Eve,

00:03:53.626 --> 00:03:57.103
Today...

00:04:27.317 --> 00:04:35.370
I should say tonight is the Christmas eve, and we are all here.

00:04:37.026 --> 00:04:43.677
We have to understand that now we have really

00:04:43.877 --> 00:04:50.041
entered into the area of Jerusalem.

00:04:53.390 --> 00:05:00.024
And where you are built in such a way,

00:05:00.224 --> 00:05:09.147
that we can understand the great incarnation of Christ.

00:05:09.347 --> 00:05:15.844
So far, He was never understood

00:05:16.045 --> 00:05:21.746
because it was a very subtle incarnation

00:05:21.946 --> 00:05:30.978
and that has made people go much away from Him,

00:05:31.178 --> 00:05:39.012
from the principle of which he was made the innocence.

00:05:44.853 --> 00:05:53.753
So today, we have to remember how he incarnated on this earth.

00:05:53.953 --> 00:05:57.994
The innocence, the auspiciousness

00:05:58.194 --> 00:06:03.603
which was filled by Adi Shakti to begin with

00:06:03.803 --> 00:06:09.312
when She started to create this universe,

00:06:09.512 --> 00:06:14.958
that He was the embodiment

00:06:15.158 --> 00:06:25.820
of all that which was so necessary before the creation started.

00:06:31.152 --> 00:06:38.681
It’s hard to understand how people could not feel it.

00:06:43.123 --> 00:06:48.668
They all have suffered so much.

00:06:52.434 --> 00:06:58.027
Whatever it is, for the Divine they do not suffer

00:06:59.892 --> 00:07:05.793
and they come on this earth to show how stupid we are,

00:07:05.994 --> 00:07:09.457
how we have not been able,

00:07:09.681 --> 00:07:14.869
to see the Truth, to see the reality.

00:07:15.843 --> 00:07:23.531
But we repeat the mistakes again and again,

00:07:23.732 --> 00:07:28.338
because we do not know ourselves,

00:07:28.539 --> 00:07:33.656
which is the only instrument by which you can know the Divine.

00:07:34.795 --> 00:07:41.671
And when we do not know
ourselves we cannot understand the Divine.

00:07:45.379 --> 00:07:51.564
Still, it’s such a great thing to see so many of you are

00:07:51.765 --> 00:08:00.580
there in that subtle area of the Spirit.

00:08:00.781 --> 00:08:05.798
That you have the sensitivity, that you can feel,

00:08:05.999 --> 00:08:11.919
the beauty of their lives, the greatness, the purity,

00:08:12.119 --> 00:08:20.219
the innocence of these great incarnations who came on this earth.

00:08:25.588 --> 00:08:31.234
But with all that, we have a very great responsibility also.

00:08:31.435 --> 00:08:33.990
Christ had only 12 disciples

00:08:34.191 --> 00:08:37.908
who didn’t even get their Realization till Christ lived.

00:08:38.109 --> 00:08:42.658
Afterwards they got Realization – 12 of them.

00:08:42.859 --> 00:08:47.652
And imagine, somebody like Thomas came to India.

00:08:47.853 --> 00:08:50.585
So, how they took so much
responsibility.

00:08:50.786 --> 00:08:54.689
They were just ordinary fishermen.

00:08:54.890 --> 00:08:58.243
They didn’t care for anything else,
but they thought, "This is the Truth

00:08:58.443 --> 00:09:06.062
and that we have to spread
this, this is our responsibility."

00:09:07.393 --> 00:09:10.236
We are so many.

00:09:10.437 --> 00:09:16.390
That is our responsibility. Is not only to enjoy yourself,

00:09:16.591 --> 00:09:23.670
but to spread Sahaja Yoga
and to practice it.

00:09:23.871 --> 00:09:31.138
Moreover, to have an ideal life,

00:09:31.339 --> 00:09:38.963
that people could see us: how we behave, how we talk,

00:09:39.164 --> 00:09:44.303
how we treat each other, how we love each other,

00:09:44.504 --> 00:09:50.834
how we understand each other, how we run to help each other –

00:09:51.035 --> 00:09:55.575
like one body.

00:09:57.105 --> 00:10:04.307
The message of Christ’s life is love.

00:10:04.508 --> 00:10:08.738
He openly talked about it.

00:10:08.939 --> 00:10:13.199
Before that, I don’t think any
incarnation talked like that,

00:10:13.400 --> 00:10:18.218
in that manner, so openly.

00:10:18.419 --> 00:10:22.180
He told His disciples that, "The greatest
joy for Me

00:10:22.381 --> 00:10:26.932
is to see that you love each other."

00:10:27.133 --> 00:10:33.588
All those things that have really made our society,

00:10:33.789 --> 00:10:39.858
made our lives miserable of jealousies and pettiness,

00:10:40.059 --> 00:10:46.587
small-mindedness has to go.
Otherwise you are not Sahaja Yogis.

00:10:46.788 --> 00:10:50.110
Where is the time for jealousy?

00:10:50.311 --> 00:10:54.588
There is no mind, this…

00:10:54.789 --> 00:11:00.389
that can see those things, anymore.

00:11:00.590 --> 00:11:02.735
So, all of us have to evolve,

00:11:02.996 --> 00:11:08.574
and the sign of evolution is not how
much we can talk about Sahaja Yoga,

00:11:08.775 --> 00:11:13.848
how much we can practice Sahaja Yoga,

00:11:14.049 --> 00:11:16.872
how much we spread Sahaja Yoga.

00:11:17.073 --> 00:11:20.596
That’s not the sign, don’t be convinced by that.

00:11:20.797 --> 00:11:31.603
But the sign of Sahaja Yoga is that
how much we can love each other,

00:11:31.804 --> 00:11:37.228
how much we understand each other,

00:11:37.429 --> 00:11:44.806
how much we can endure for others with great joy

00:11:45.007 --> 00:11:50.087
and how much we do not bother about ourselves,

00:11:50.288 --> 00:11:54.517
our families, our children.

00:11:54.718 --> 00:12:02.593
This ‘mine, my, me’ has to go.

00:12:03.104 --> 00:12:07.219
It doesn’t go by saying "go". It’s a state, again.

00:12:07.419 --> 00:12:16.301
But then only you should be
convinced, "Now I am a Sahaja Yogi!"

00:12:20.105 --> 00:12:24.191
Christ has said, "Love thy neighbor as thyself!"

00:12:24.392 --> 00:12:27.761
I would say that

00:12:27.962 --> 00:12:32.456
you have to love every Sahaja Yogi as yourself,

00:12:32.657 --> 00:12:36.315
because they are part and parcel of this body.

00:12:36.516 --> 00:12:40.322
You cannot afford to hate someone.

00:12:40.523 --> 00:12:46.853
Of course, those who are useless are thrown out of the body.

00:12:47.054 --> 00:12:52.152
But those who are there living, you must love them.

00:12:52.353 --> 00:12:56.083
I think this is the message of Christ

00:12:56.284 --> 00:13:01.557
and other message is absolute morality,

00:13:01.758 --> 00:13:07.174
absolute morality.

00:13:07.920 --> 00:13:12.969
As He has said that, "Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes"

00:13:13.169 --> 00:13:16.685
is such a subtle thing to say,

00:13:16.886 --> 00:13:22.103
that you should not have eyes which have adultery in them.

00:13:22.304 --> 00:13:28.729
It doesn’t mean only for women but it also mean for things.

00:13:28.930 --> 00:13:31.410
It also means for properties,

00:13:31.611 --> 00:13:35.749
it also means for the success of others.

00:13:35.950 --> 00:13:40.459
Adultery means the one where you try to aggress

00:13:40.660 --> 00:13:45.692
and to be greedy about it.

00:13:48.422 --> 00:13:53.952
If there is greed or if there is lust in your eyes,

00:13:54.153 --> 00:13:59.175
then it’s an adulterous eyes.

00:14:00.097 --> 00:14:03.491
It is very subtle, I know.

00:14:03.692 --> 00:14:11.295
It is very subtle
and the attention is the best way

00:14:11.496 --> 00:14:14.988
which communicates to you

00:14:15.189 --> 00:14:22.554
whether you are above lust and greed or not.

00:14:22.916 --> 00:14:27.628
But the more you try to rise above these things,

00:14:27.829 --> 00:14:34.283
your heart opens and you start
enjoying your virtues, your morality.

00:14:34.483 --> 00:14:39.049
You enjoy, you don’t think you are moral, you don’t think that way,

00:14:39.250 --> 00:14:46.810
but you enjoy that state where you
are really moral because you are moral.

00:14:47.011 --> 00:14:50.023
You just enjoy yourself.

00:14:50.224 --> 00:14:53.433
It’s a headache to be interested in some
woman,

00:14:53.634 --> 00:14:59.981
interested in some man. It’s a headache. It’s a joyless pursuit.

00:15:00.182 --> 00:15:04.486
And once you are detached,

00:15:04.687 --> 00:15:12.918
the joy is complete,

00:15:13.119 --> 00:15:18.966
because you are one with reality, pure reality.

00:15:19.167 --> 00:15:31.099
There is no inhibitions, no
restrictions, no taboos, – nothing,

00:15:31.300 --> 00:15:37.594
but just you are that!
Nobody has to tell you.

00:15:37.795 --> 00:15:40.305
If you are gold, you are gold.

00:15:40.506 --> 00:15:45.127
Nobody has to tell you, "Now,
you don’t behave like non-gold",

00:15:45.328 --> 00:15:48.990
you are gold, so you are gold.

00:15:49.191 --> 00:15:52.224
That’s the power!

00:15:52.425 --> 00:15:59.588
And the power of a Sahaja Yogi is
that he is the purest form of human being.

00:15:59.789 --> 00:16:04.341
Without the power what are we? Nothing.

00:16:05.406 --> 00:16:08.356
The purest form

00:16:08.557 --> 00:16:15.023
and in the purest form of love

00:16:15.224 --> 00:16:21.279
you get the purest form of knowledge.

00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:29.599
This is kaivalya is the,
absolute knowledge

00:16:29.800 --> 00:16:36.917
and absolute love,

00:16:37.118 --> 00:16:42.657
detached, pure.

00:16:46.753 --> 00:16:57.151
That time when you are in that state,

00:16:57.352 --> 00:17:04.872
you just watch anything, see anything,

00:17:05.073 --> 00:17:10.807
all the power of giving joy from everything

00:17:11.097 --> 00:17:13.410
just starts bubbling into you

00:17:13.611 --> 00:17:18.844
and you don’t see the bad things at all, you never see the bad things.

00:17:23.229 --> 00:17:27.379
The power of enjoying everything

00:17:27.579 --> 00:17:32.522
is the power of Sahaja Yogis, to enjoy everything.

00:17:35.799 --> 00:17:38.784
Anything can be enjoyed,

00:17:38.985 --> 00:17:42.234
any small thing can be enjoyed,

00:17:42.435 --> 00:17:45.038
any big thing can be enjoyed.

00:17:45.239 --> 00:17:51.568
But impurities one cannot enjoy,
immorality you cannot enjoy.

00:17:51.769 --> 00:17:56.781
It’s not enjoyment, it’s just a fascination
maybe, I don’t know what it is called as,

00:17:56.982 --> 00:18:00.226
as I cannot enjoy then I don’t know what it
is.

00:18:00.427 --> 00:18:06.366
But what you enjoy really is the purity of another personality,

00:18:06.567 --> 00:18:09.370
the purity of this,

00:18:09.570 --> 00:18:16.138
all that is done by someone with such pure heart.

00:18:16.507 --> 00:18:24.201
And the deeper you see,
it becomes simpler and simpler.

00:18:24.401 --> 00:18:32.073
Then you don’t say smart things, no, you
don’t, don’t have to show off, nothing.

00:18:32.274 --> 00:18:36.762
You just say simple, sweet nice things.

00:18:36.963 --> 00:18:43.988
It’s so touching, so beautiful,

00:18:44.189 --> 00:18:50.545
but must allow the deeper love within us to come out.

00:18:50.746 --> 00:18:56.472
Many people love also but they don’t know how to express it.

00:18:56.689 --> 00:18:59.180
There are many people who are misunderstood,

00:18:59.381 --> 00:19:02.558
because they don’t know how to express their love.

00:19:02.759 --> 00:19:10.511
In Sahaja Yoga you have to
learn the yukti, the technique.

00:19:10.712 --> 00:19:14.805
"Yukti" is a very sweet word, not technique is not,

00:19:15.006 --> 00:19:18.862
technique deals with something very materialistic.

00:19:19.063 --> 00:19:23.484
But yukti means the trick, trick of the trade,

00:19:23.685 --> 00:19:31.954
what to say when that would really just pierce,

00:19:32.155 --> 00:19:39.947
like a dart in the heart of someone, the beautiful feeling.

00:19:42.008 --> 00:19:46.979
That one has to understand and practice.

00:19:47.180 --> 00:19:51.569
All little-little things here and there,

00:19:51.770 --> 00:20:00.424
little turning here and there is
an art of living a Sahaja Yoga life.

00:20:00.625 --> 00:20:04.780
And I’ve seen children say such sweet-sweet things.

00:20:04.981 --> 00:20:08.947
That’s why Christ has said that, "You have to be like children

00:20:09.148 --> 00:20:14.548
to enter into the Kingdom of God", but I
would say, "to stay in the Kingdom of God.

00:20:14.897 --> 00:20:22.415
You have to be simple like children, deep and simple."

00:20:23.849 --> 00:20:32.232
This seminar, or whatever you may call
it, Ganapatipule, I don’t know what you call,

00:20:32.433 --> 00:20:40.654
is a Divine congregation of all the Gods and Goddesses,

00:20:40.855 --> 00:20:45.568
is very symbolic to Me,

00:20:45.769 --> 00:20:50.519
because this represents the whole world,

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:57.589
it represents the problems of the
whole world and also the solutions.

00:20:57.790 --> 00:21:01.625
It’s such a beautiful idea.

00:21:01.826 --> 00:21:06.236
I don’t know how it worked into
My head that I started this kind of a,

00:21:06.437 --> 00:21:14.230
beautiful congregation to meet you all.

00:21:14.431 --> 00:21:19.819
It was very nice yesterday, you kept
awake all the while and came to see Me.

00:21:20.019 --> 00:21:24.755
I could meet all of you and I could have some rapport.

00:21:24.955 --> 00:21:27.658
I couldn’t say much, I was just smiling at you,

00:21:27.859 --> 00:21:31.671
but just I could express My
love and you gave Me that chance.

00:21:31.872 --> 00:21:35.786
I must thank you very much for that.
